Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.24,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:14.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:18.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:23.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:30.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:33.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:36.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:44.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:15.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:18.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,160.389)}The Terrifying Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,700.389)}of Doctor Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:28.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meteors fly to Earth from space,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:32.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,where they enter Earth's atmosphere\Nand release heat and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:33.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the origin of shooting stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.25,0:01:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Romantic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's shining...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little bit creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Katsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Katsuo was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, help m...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment was a roaring success.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's incredible science allows\Nus to control meteors in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, we'll sow panic by dropping\Nmeteorites all over Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, all over Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A toast to the completion\Nof the new machine model.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi, shall we test it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cyclone Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:42.63,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Race, race, machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:46.34,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Soar like a shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:53.57,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Let the jets of your engine roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:57.25,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Crush those evil monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.84,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Charge, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:04.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Race into the flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:08.25,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Hurricane Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:11.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Hurricane Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:14.86,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Fight, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:19.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:27.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Race, race, machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:31.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Run like lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:38.02,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,And carry all our hopes with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,300 kilometers per hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's test the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. It performs well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see Rider's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we blew him to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider is invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you bringing meteorites to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A new Shocker monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidevil, the devil-trainer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times must\Nwe fight before you learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cyborgs who serve evil will never triumph!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick Counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rider Kick won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Squidevil...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is its weak point?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Takeshi doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of having a\Nnew machine at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's taking his time trying\Nto get the most out of the new machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's acting strangely...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me, Hongo! Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had even more training\Nin ways to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will be victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Squidevil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo. Speak to me, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're covered in sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who was it they sent at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A terrifying cyborg, enhanced\Nthrough Shocker training...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rider Kick won't work on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker has something that powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he'll beat me if\NI don't do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, will you train with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Training? You're in no condition for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't do it, I'll ask Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The area's changed a lot, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it has, in every way possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But what never changes is human dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I still dream of winning\Nthe World Grand Prix.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm the same way, Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've both been in\Nthat business for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me. I want\Nto show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A brand new machine I just completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place I want to stop by first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great. Name the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,An ex-racer and an observatory...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an odd combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll be right back.\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:16.22,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60\3c&H254A59&\c&H151D22&}Tokyo Observatory
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumaki! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:29.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Tachibana Tobei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:35.48,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is Shocker's Japanese\Ncyborg training center.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,From this day forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you will act as a trainer\Nfor Shocker's cyborgs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Tobei will never serve Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Show him to the training center.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumaki! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Agree to be a Shocker trainer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in your hands, Trainer Kumaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumaki... I'm disappointed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sold your soul to the devil,\Nand became a Shocker trainer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder you\Nbetrayed your old friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to understand, Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They would have killed me\Nif I hadn't agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to live, even\Nif it's in a party of devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have a chance to\Nmake my dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can keep racing\Nin a world fallen to Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Say yes, Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way to save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider will come to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But until you agree to be a trainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker won't challenge Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll remain locked up in here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to get Rider's help\Nis to become a Shocker trainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do this, or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:52.27,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru, Naoki! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cool, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being just like Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you love Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't you realize how\Ndangerous the Rider Kick is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Kamen Rider can\Nperform the Rider Kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond the abilities\Nof children like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just get hurt. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the danger Kamen\NRider's training exposes him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! I'm all ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what training\NSquidevil is going through...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your back into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, jump higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your entire body! All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think you'll beat Kamen\NRider that way, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Use all your power! All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ram into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me. There's\Na remote control in my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:14:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A remote control?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So his weak point is his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider's really something, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder where Rider went...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? You both saw it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't try to be Rider anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown us how dangerous it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you got the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency!\NEmergency, Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Another cockroach in the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss's car just came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But he wasn't inside it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops wasn't inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be a time bomb inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.63,Italics,,0,0,0,,No fear of that, Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.23,Italics,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Tobei is in the hands of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:49.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,One reason alone: to make\Nthe Kamen Rider fight Squidevil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:51.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:55.91,Italics,,0,0,0,,If you wish to save Tobei\NTachibana, get into this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.24,Italics,,0,0,0,,We'll tell you where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.43,Italics,,0,0,0,,I've done everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.76,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's all up to you now, Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana, get to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't watch Shocker's\Nshooting stars tear it to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then you are...\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go with me. Let's escape together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kumaki! Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we got to spend\Na little more time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Squidevil is in the Fujimi Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to fight the Kamen Rider there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Their shooting star plan...\Ncan be prevented if you defeat Squidevil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kumaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've come, Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Tachibana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect Shocker to keep its promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Tobei will be\NShocker's slave until his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The brat, Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Hongo Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the Kamen Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Squidevil?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Squidevil will face you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... see how you deal with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:04.34,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.84,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:11.91,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:15.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:19.05,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:22.45,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:25.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.89,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:33.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:37.05,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... he can't handle it after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,His weak point is his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't win this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The shooting stars\Nare nearing the Earth now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, Japan will be in ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He broke my remote controller!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Drill Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have beaten him all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:55.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's commander-in-chief,\NDoctor Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:22:57.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,was secretly the monstrous Squidevil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:02.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Kamen Rider fought hard and\Nfoiled their terrible shooting star plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:05.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:08.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker will never stop trying\Nto ruin our peaceful world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.09,Cont,,0,60,150,,{\blur.8}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:13.26,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(320.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.96,0:23:16.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:17.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Girakorogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:21.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sharp red nails stand in Rider's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:24.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What horror is Shocker planning\Nwith those nails of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:31.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The Monstrous\NGirakorogi's Nails of Death."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:31.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs115\bord0.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,720.389)}The Monstrous Girakorogi's \NNails of Death
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:40.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.38,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:45.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:48.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:50.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:52.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:55.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:03.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.97,0:24:07.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:11.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:15.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Terrifying Truth of Doctor Shinigami?